data.description: This 2 Bedroom + Den (easily converted to 3rd BR)  fabulous ''Bella'' model pool home features a serene lake view and very tastefully upgraded decor. It is better than new, so why wait for construction uncertainties? Walk in and notice the porcelain wood look tile flooring throughout. Cook will delight in this beautiful kitchen, with upgraded espresso cabinets with crowns, quartz countertops, subway tile backsplash, SS appliances, a farm sink & a cozy breakfast nook. Modern living at its best with a great open room with a dining area adorned with decorative wall and ceiling moldings. 2 custom closets spacious owner's suite with seamless showers & elegant lighting & fan fixtures. Enjoy the outdoor Florida lifestyle on your brick patio & enjoy your saltwater pool. Furniture Negotiable. Call! Verano has all desired community amenities: a 27-court pickleball facility, walking paths, indoor and outdoor pools, fitness centers, a sauna, a dog park, tennis courts, a social clubhouse, and so much more. HOA dues include basic cable, internet, alarm monitoring, common area maintenance, and access to the amenity centers.
